---
title: Speedy BBQ Pork and Pepper Braised Beans with Buttery Toasties
description: This one is for all the pork-and-beans fans! Sweet and smoky BBQ-charred pork chops adorn the quickest braised beans you've ever made. It's served up with ciabatta toasties to help mop up all that goodness.
